## Architecture — Stateless Execution Pattern

This MCP server follows the **stateless execution** pattern: each tool call is
independent, no shared state between calls, deterministic output for the same
input. Best suited for tools that transform input → output without side effects.

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle
    idle --> running: tool.invoke
    running --> completed: success
    running --> failed: error
    completed --> idle
    failed --> idle
    completed --> [*]
```

