## Install

```bash
# using uv (recommended)
uv pip install -e .

# or with pip
pip install -e .
```

## Run as MCP server

### Claude Desktop / Cursor

Add to `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{name}}": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "{{snakeCase name}}.server"]
    }
  }
}
```

### Standalone (stdio)
```bash
python -m {{snakeCase name}}.server
```

## Test

```bash
pytest -v --cov={{snakeCase name}} --cov-report=term-missing
mutmut run                    # mutation testing
hypothesis --version          # property-based tests already in tests/
```

## Lifecycle (FSM)

State machine lives in `.mcp/state/`. Transitions are materialized via
GitHub Actions workflows in `.github/workflows/`.

| State | Description |
|---|---|
| `idle` | Server running, awaiting tool call |
| `running` | Tool executing |
| `completed` | Tool returned successfully |
| `failed` | Tool raised error |

